President Abdel Fattah El Sisi issued a decree, approving an agreement to boost technical cooperation between Egypt and Germany. The deal was signed on June 12, 2017. In another decree, the president approved a loan agreement signed by the Investment and International Cooperation Ministry and Germany's KfW Development Bank to carry out economic reforms in Egypt. The two decrees were published in the official gazette on Thursday 15 /3/2018. MENA